headline: Illinois American Water Announces 2025 Firefighter Grant Program
summary: BELLEVILLE, Ill., August 13, 2025--Illinois American Water announced today that it is accepting applications for its 2025 Firefighter Grant Program. Deadline to apply is September 19.
